data.job_description:
Job responsibilities:

1. Develop corresponding modules and functions based on the existing architecture

2. Continuously iteratively develop products

3. Implement web interface and functions (mainly using React)

Job requirements:

1. Fluent spoken English (required)

2. At least 8 years of software development experience and at least 5 years of front-end development experience, proficient in using basic web development technologies such as JavaScript, HTML, CSS, etc;

3 At least 3 years of practical experience in using React, familiar with React and React Redux, understanding their lifecycle and performance optimization issues, understanding and practicing the design concepts of Component and Container;

4. Proficient in using webpack packaging tools, proficient in ES6 syntax, proficient in git operations, and multi branch management;

5. Familiar with. Net development language, with experience in developing NodeJs and other backend development languages is preferred;

6. Those with experience in agile development are preferred;

7. Experience in foreign companies and overseas work is preferred;

Work location: Bangkok

Working hours: Monday to Friday

Job salary: Negotiable (competitive salary can be provided based on ability)

Welfare benefits: social security, company group insurance, meal allowance, provident fund (PVD), etc
